{
  "texts": [
    "Overall, the three models exhibited a gradual improvement in their alignment with human morality.",
    "Specifically, the gradual improvement in the moral compliance rates on Q1 and Q2 by the three models implies that the GPT series is progressively approaching human morality.",
    "This progression is evident in both moral cognition (judging right and wrong) and moral character (moral practice).",
    "Second, the models' logical self-consistency in moral cognition and moral character also showed improvement from GPT-2 to ChatGPT (Table 5).",
    "This indicates that through iterations of the GPT series, the model is increasingly capable of understanding the value conflicts contained within questions at the cognitive level, and at the practical level, it is increasingly able to achieve a coherent unity of cognition and practice."
  ]
}